    "Id": "chassisdef_sarissa_MN2-A",
    "Name": "Sarissa",
    "Details": "This is an updated version of the MN1-K that has been rebuilt using an IndustrialMech production line. It keeps the same weapons configuration as the MN1-D but replaces the primitive engine, primitive armor, and primitive cockpit with more modern upgrades. It's protected by heavy industrial armor, adds an ejection seat so the pilot can escape, increases the amount of single heat sinks to 18, and upgrades the engine to a 200 fusion engine.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.79</color></b>",
    "Icon": "sasquash"
  },
